quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  15,80,Netoto Abandu ba Hijri bayingasia Abarumwa
  15,81,Ne nikhubahelesia abimanyisio biefu nabo nibalabukulamwo oluchendo tawe
  15,82,Ne bakwotanga tsingulu nibakasia tsinzu
  15,83,Mana eshinyasio shioluyoka nishibabukula mumabwibwi
  15,84,Mana akabakholanga nikalabakhonyakhwo shiosi shiosi tawe
  15,85,"Ne shikhwalonga likulu nende eshialo nende ebili hakari wabio halali khubwatoto, ne toto indukho iliula , kho leshela okhuleshela okhulayi"
  15,86,Toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi niye omuloonji ne niye Omumanyi muno
  15,87,Ne khwakhwelesia tsinyaali saba tsisomungwa ebise nebise nende Ikurani yoluyali
  15,88,"Ne olakhosia tsimoni tsitsio khukalia akakhwahelesia emikanda chindi hakari wabu, nohomba olababelelela tawe. Ne wishilie abasuubili olubaa lulwo. (lwetsimbabaasi)"
  15,89,"Ne boolambu:“ toto esie nesie Omwikanyilisi Omwinoosi.(owahabulafu)"
  15,90,Shingala khweshilia balia (eshinyasio bosi) balia abekaba emikanda (okhwikalila abusalamu)
  15,91,Balia bakhola Ikurani okhuba omubunjikho kwobubeyi
  15,92,Kho nditsuba khu Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi mbu khulibareeba bosi
  15,93,Khukalia koosi akabakholanga
  15,94,Kho yusia akawalomesibwa ne obe ehale nende Abatsokaasi
  15,95,Toto efwe khukhuyela okhulinda nende abakhubayilanga
  15,96,Balia abatsokasinjia Nyasaye nende Abanyasaye bandi balitsa okhumanya
  15,97,Netoto khwamanya mbu eshilifu shishio shinyoolanga obusiro khukalia akababoolanga
  15,98,"Kho tswenula Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi khulwa okhumwitsoomia , ne obe halala nende bamwinamilanga nibasujuda"
  15,99,Ne olaame Nyasaye wuwo okhuula likhuulile eliatoto elo . (lifwa)